data.title: Andertons Music Co.
data.meta_description: Browse all Guitar Dept at Andertons Music Co. Over 15,000 instruments with free next-day UK delivery, interest-free finance and amazing deals!
data.text:
We love the electric guitar and we’ve been selling them for over 55 years now. So, you could say that we know a thing or two about what's good and what's bad! Take a look at our massive selection in the knowledge that our stock has been curated to include the finest instruments that money can buy — at any price-point!

No instrument has inspired so many to start rocking as the electric guitar. Here at Andertons, we've got iconic electric guitars like the Fender Stratocaster, Telecaster and the Gibson Les Paul — instruments that you would see gracing stages the world over.

What if you want something with a different look and sound? Well, we’ve got hard-thrashing ESP guitars, Ibanez for the shredders and Jackson for the metalheads. We also stock Chapman Guitars and Reverend for players who want a high-quality, versatile electric guitars at a lower price.

If you prefer a boutique approach, we offer the ever-incredible PRS guitars with their exquisite timbers and contemporary look, as well as limited edition guitars from the Fender Custom Shop & Gibson Custom Shop.

Find the right electric guitar for you at Andertons!
